com.atakmap.android.gui

Class PanPreference

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.preference.Preference
      • com.atakmap.android.gui.PanPreference
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<android.preference.Preference>

    public class PanPreference
extends android.preference.Preference
    Plugin aware preference that correctly handles Summary and Title information. This has been modified to allow for a pluginIcon attribute which will allow for icons to be used in the entity.
